<paragraph id="2F0342E01897EEEF736114DE1662BBC0" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Doppeltgefiederter Reiherschnabel</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="8CA2AC49C18E7FF3E2633EE27A676A21" pageId="null" pageNumber="630" type="description">
<paragraph id="C76E829CC64E19F5EE0F4DB2DA8E2541" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="1F7A1F7DDBB18D67845553E3A73951E6" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Geraniaceae" genus="Erodium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Geraniales" pageId="null" pageNumber="630" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cicutarium">
<emphasis id="C006C45FA5C2C0F8F1D453B45C5158B5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">E. cicutarium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1) durch folgende Merkmale: Pflanze 3-20 cm hoch, dicht behaart (auch 
<normalizedToken id="C9D07EAFBB0FCEB922851AD98E6B0197" originalValue="Drüsenhaare" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Druesenhaare</normalizedToken>
!); Stengel meist aufrecht, Blattabschnitte bis zum Mittelnerv geteilt; 
<normalizedToken id="8F671E62E3734B1391C2B88699EC8463" originalValue="Blütenstände" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Bluetenstaende</normalizedToken>
2-3 
<normalizedToken id="6607622C13C57286C8B880FED352A8E2" originalValue="blütig" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">bluetig</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="9093FEA89D24E76A6189F82020EEC081" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
3,5-4 mm lang; 
<emphasis id="15A4B01B63EDDD1944AAEABBD7B07C46" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">
<normalizedToken id="C4CC18B6B7770A393D4D74A78DE0A1CE" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
4-5 mm lang, 
<normalizedToken id="4A82C77C912A801F10D9AFEB57DE6A74" originalValue="blaßrosa" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">blassrosa</normalizedToken>
, nicht dunkel gefleckt; Frucht
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="F5586623969F916AFCBA4F668C40E7ED" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">mit Schnabel</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="BA6EB69937BF4661DD1775CABDE221E8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">
2-3 cm lang, ohne 
<normalizedToken id="1A41BB16A72879AE463EAFE613D8C08A" originalValue="ringförmige" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">ringfoermige</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="C2471DCD38419C7D89BE177D883FFFD3" originalValue="Einschnürung" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Einschnuerung</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="2B05AFA8E3CD4D1DF7894A32E0615842" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="FD809FB750DC5FA8AAA60E4961B0C144" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="BE3CDF21C56CB456D830353B6083B24B" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1729FFD0CF283B71E6C58A68C6A60F90" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">
<emphasis id="1D34BE244A00D3228B8E625D991CFFE3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="195B5064A7973F83C98CAD7F55A54108" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">20:</emphasis>
Material aus Westeuropa (Warburg 1938, 
<normalizedToken id="B07988BAFFBC59A4F6D7470CB9EBF085" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="C023D0EE7F74B67CDAEF97C2276EE6E8" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1944b, Andreas 1947, Rottgardt 1956, Larsen 1958c, Guittonneau 1966).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EA58093B413672FE905C89A76082B3DB" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">
<emphasis id="94D95DDA767786B1132838B4CC020195" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Sandige 
<normalizedToken id="1459392B0F9EFA8C4D08C269C690A67D" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Boeden</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D6F792A7BCEDA609FF2A148AC976F415" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">
<emphasis id="A4A1FCE73817A092210CA1825886E26E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="7754FF76437469D02ACA6F39B99A8FD3" originalValue="Westeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Westeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="00567B47B11AE77748C40B5371812C5D" originalValue="Westeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Westeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="AAE312F2114ABB96A59A8E236379D1A1" originalValue="Küsten" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Kuesten</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="CFEBD21B5CEF2288CECAFBCE3998F6AE" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Niederlande und Italien. - Im Gebiet: Aostatal, mittleres und unteres Wallis (Vernayaz bis Visp).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D9D599A40E307C0EB77B01676DA92903" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">
<emphasis id="4A67288D9E3CDF32044341FBE3737343" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Die bisher als 
<taxonomicName id="F043F3A44CE49CEF19E225DA866D62BA" authority="Beauverd" authorityName="Beauverd" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Geraniaceae" genus="Erodium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Geraniales" pageId="null" pageNumber="630" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="cicutarium" variety="vallesiacum">
<emphasis id="1CA260686BA661CDE05B649DC63DED0B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">E. cicutarium</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="553961B8232DBADF4ACE50A01EB08F94" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">vallesiacum</emphasis>
Beauverd
</taxonomicName>
bezeichneten Pflanzen aus dem Wallis entsprechen in ihren morphologischen Merkmalen 
<emphasis id="D16DE745CF871EE17BFB410410E3E255" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">
E. 
<normalizedToken id="0D420ACD9C78405ACE73556914D58081" originalValue="bipinnätum" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">bipinnaetum</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
Eine 
<normalizedToken id="DFB5689900B959FA1EAB34F513AD98E6" originalValue="Chromosomenzählung" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Chromosomenzaehlung</normalizedToken>
ist 
<normalizedToken id="CD5F9AD7140E5AA874A05854EC50B0ED" originalValue="wünschenswert" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">wuenschenswert</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="C39961A9817352F291AFE4C75D2724D3" originalValue="Über" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">Ueber</normalizedToken>
die Abgrenzung gegen 
<taxonomicName id="037C9C1C03DB49CAF6CE1C766F23B85B" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Geraniaceae" genus="Erodium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Geraniales" pageId="null" pageNumber="630" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="cicutarium">
<emphasis id="C775D85EF139AACCAE54EE9327651B22" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="630">E. cicutarium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
und morphologisch zwischen den beiden Arten stehende Sippen vgl. die zytologischen Untersuchungen von Andreas (1947) und Larsen (1958c).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</treatment>
